gotten with her. My uncle used the Bible to help me get back on track, and to remind me of two other

00:58:52.530 --> 00:59:02.530
very important things that Jehovah was proud of me and that I was not alone. James 1, 2 and 3 says,

00:59:03.250 --> 00:59:10.210
consider it all joy my brothers when you meet with various trials, knowing as you do that this

00:59:10.210 --> 00:59:19.170
tested quality of your faith produces endurance. I think about that scripture a lot, because soon

00:59:19.170 --> 00:59:25.969
I'll probably be sent to prison for refusing military service. Being courageous with that

00:59:25.969 --> 00:59:33.250
classmate helped me build the faith and courage that I need now. I can give up anything for Jehovah.

