I really hope that Lucas is resurrected so I can show him around paradise and teach him more about

01:00:04.909 --> 01:00:15.789
Jehovah. I showed him pictures, but the real thing will be so much better. Then I can hold my baby

01:00:15.789 --> 01:00:28.130
girl again. Our program has focused on the many ways that Jehovah is with us. He's with us as we

01:00:28.130 --> 01:00:37.489
worked towards dedication and baptism. He's with us at our congregation meetings, and when we are

01:00:37.489 --> 01:00:45.489
with our spiritual family, he's with us as we successfully face persecution and hardship.

01:00:46.929 --> 01:00:53.090
And Jehovah is with us when we share the good news of his kingdom with everyone we meet.

01:00:54.449 --> 01:01:00.530
And Brother Maray, I appreciate that you were here with me for this month's program.

