01:01:16.050 --> 01:01:26.769
Africa. These islands were formed by volcanic eruptions. The highest point is the Dormantede volcano

01:01:26.769 --> 01:01:36.130
on Tenerife. Here the weather is mild and sunny throughout the year. This is made to Canary

01:01:36.210 --> 01:01:45.869
Islands famous for their extensive banana plantations. Tenerife is a popular tourist destination.

01:01:46.590 --> 01:01:54.510
