01:01:54.510 --> 01:02:04.590
the beaches, the lush terrain, and the food. The island of Tenerife has 33 congregations,

01:02:05.309 --> 01:02:13.630
and more than 3,000 publishers. 492 of whom are regular pioneers.

01:02:14.989 --> 01:02:20.989
