over 15 languages, including Russian, German, French, Hindi, and Romanian. They preach

01:02:39.280 --> 01:02:45.119
everywhere in the cities, as well as the rural and mountainous regions.

01:02:45.920 --> 01:02:53.760
Our brothers and sisters in Tenerife send you their warm, Christian love and greetings.

